" See below for feature list
" https://github.com/XVimProject/XVim2/blob/master/Documents/Users/FeatureList.md

set number " show line numbers
set incsearch " inline highlighting
set hlsearch " highlight search
set ignorecase " ignore case in search

" map backspace and return to move faster in a file
nnoremap <BS> 10k
onoremap <BS> 10k
vnoremap <BS> 10k
nnoremap <CR> 10j
onoremap <CR> 10j
vnoremap <CR> 10j

" Navigation
nmap <space>n :nissue<CR>
nmap <space>p :pissue<CR>

" Show
nmap <space>f :xccmd showInFinder<CR>

" Toggle Toolbars
nmap <space>h :xccmd toggleNavigatorsVisibility<CR>
nmap <space>j :xccmd toggleDebuggerVisibility<CR>
nmap <space>l :xccmd toggleUtilitiesVisibility<CR>
